{
  "video_id": "1AT5klu_yAQ",
  "title": "Confessions of a recovering micromanager | Chieh Huang",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 15496.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m really here to do today is talk to you about micromanagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15520.0,
      "end_time": 17736.0,
      "text": "and what I learned about micromanagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17760.0,
      "end_time": 21456.0,
      "text": "by being a micromanager over the last few years of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21480.0,
      "end_time": 23576.0,
      "text": "But first off, what is micromanagement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23600.0,
      "end_time": 25816.0,
      "text": "How do we really define it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 29976.0,
      "text": "Well, I posit that it&#39;s actually taking great, wonderful, imaginative people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30000.0,
      "end_time": 31216.0,
      "text": "like all of you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31240.0,
      "end_time": 33135.0,
      "text": "bringing them in into an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33160.0,
      "end_time": 34736.0,
      "text": "and then crushing their souls --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34760.0,
      "end_time": 35976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36000.0,
      "end_time": 37856.0,
      "text": "by telling them what font size to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37880.0,
      "end_time": 39536.0,
      "text": "In the history of mankind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39560.0,
      "end_time": 41376.0,
      "text": "has anyone ever said this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 41400.0,
      "end_time": 45856.0,
      "text": "\"John, we were never going to close that deal with Times New Roman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45880.0,
      "end_time": 48736.0,
      "text": "but because you insisted on Helvetica --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48760.0,
      "end_time": 50135.0,
      "text": "bam!"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50160.0,
      "end_time": 51376.0,
      "text": "Dotted line --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51400.0,
      "end_time": 53135.0,
      "text": "millions of dollars started to flow."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 53160.0,
      "end_time": 54535.0,
      "text": "That was the missing piece!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54560.0,
      "end_time": 56560.0,
      "text": "No one&#39;s ever said that, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56800.0,
      "end_time": 59576.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s actually physical manifestations that we probably see in ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59600.0,
      "end_time": 60856.0,
      "text": "by being micromanaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60880.0,
      "end_time": 63936.0,
      "text": "Think about the most tired you&#39;ve ever been in your life, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 63960.0,
      "end_time": 66536.0,
      "text": "It probably wasn&#39;t when you stayed the latest at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66560.0,
      "end_time": 69960.0,
      "text": "or it wasn&#39;t when you came home from a road trip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69120.0,
      "end_time": 72616.0,
      "text": "it was probably when you had someone looking over your shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72640.0,
      "end_time": 75480.0,
      "text": "watching your each and every move."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 76400.0,
      "end_time": 78856.0,
      "text": "Kind of like my mother-in-law when she&#39;s over right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78880.0,
      "end_time": 79896.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79920.0,
      "end_time": 81616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m like, \"I got this,\" you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81640.0,
      "end_time": 83776.0,
      "text": "And so there&#39;s actually data to support this."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83800.0,
      "end_time": 85776.0,
      "text": "There was a recent study in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 85800.0,
      "end_time": 87936.0,
      "text": "They took 100 hospital employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87960.0,
      "end_time": 89616.0,
      "text": "put an activity tracker on them"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 89640.0,
      "end_time": 93560.0,
      "text": "and then let them go about their next 12-hour shift all alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93800.0,
      "end_time": 95560.0,
      "text": "just a regular 12-hour shift."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 98616.0,
      "text": "At the end of the shift, they asked them, \"Do you feel fatigued?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98640.0,
      "end_time": 101960.0,
      "text": "And what they found was actually really interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101120.0,
      "end_time": 103536.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t necessarily the people who moved the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103560.0,
      "end_time": 104936.0,
      "text": "that felt the most fatigued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 104960.0,
      "end_time": 108240.0,
      "text": "but it was the folks that didn&#39;t have control over their jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109120.0,
      "end_time": 112456.0,
      "text": "So if we know that micromanagement isn&#39;t really effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112480.0,
      "end_time": 114256.0,
      "text": "why do we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114280.0,
      "end_time": 115976.0,
      "text": "Is it that the definition is wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116000.0,
      "end_time": 118416.0,
      "text": "I posited that micromanagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 118440.0,
      "end_time": 121456.0,
      "text": "is just bringing in great, wonderful, imaginative people"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 121480.0,
      "end_time": 122936.0,
      "text": "and then crushing their souls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122960.0,
      "end_time": 124936.0,
      "text": "so is it that we actually want to hire --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124960.0,
      "end_time": 126336.0,
      "text": "deep down inside of us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 126360.0,
      "end_time": 128199.0,
      "text": "dull and unimaginative people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132136.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one of those questions you probably don&#39;t even need to ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 132160.0,
      "end_time": 135335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like, \"Do you want to get your luggage stolen at the airport?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 135360.0,
      "end_time": 137576.0,
      "text": "Probably not, but I&#39;ve never been asked, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 137600.0,
      "end_time": 140150.0,
      "text": "So has anyone asked you, as a manager,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 140390.0,
      "end_time": 142856.0,
      "text": "\"Do you want to hire dull and unimaginative people?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 142880.0,
      "end_time": 145816.0,
      "text": "So, I don&#39;t know, this is TED, we better back it up with data."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 145840.0,
      "end_time": 148576.0,
      "text": "We actually asked hundreds of people around the country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 148600.0,
      "end_time": 150600.0,
      "text": "hundreds of managers across the country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 150624.0,
      "end_time": 153184.0,
      "text": "do you want to hire dull and unimaginative people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154000.0,
      "end_time": 155856.0,
      "text": "Alright, it&#39;s an interesting question."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 155880.0,
      "end_time": 157536.0,
      "text": "Well, interesting results as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 157560.0,
      "end_time": 158816.0,
      "text": "So, 94% said no --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 158840.0,
      "end_time": 160560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 160800.0,
      "end_time": 162976.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t want to hire dull and unimaginative people."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 163000.0,
      "end_time": 165576.0,
      "text": "Six percent probably didn&#39;t understand the question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 167296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167320.0,
      "end_time": 168576.0,
      "text": "but, bless their hearts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 168600.0,
      "end_time": 171536.0,
      "text": "maybe they do just want to hire dull and unimaginative people."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171560.0,
      "end_time": 175256.0,
      "text": "But 94 percent said they did not, and so why do we do this still then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 175280.0,
      "end_time": 177896.0,
      "text": "Well, I posit that it&#39;s something really, really simple"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 177920.0,
      "end_time": 181655.0,
      "text": "that all of us deep down inside know and have actually felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181680.0,
      "end_time": 183776.0,
      "text": "So when we get hired into an organization --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183800.0,
      "end_time": 185856.0,
      "text": "it could be a club, it could be a law firm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185880.0,
      "end_time": 189256.0,
      "text": "it could be a school organization, it could be anything --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189280.0,
      "end_time": 192960.0,
      "text": "no one ever jumps to the top of the totem pole, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 192120.0,
      "end_time": 193936.0,
      "text": "You start at the very bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193960.0,
      "end_time": 195176.0,
      "text": "Doing what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 195200.0,
      "end_time": 196416.0,
      "text": "Doing work."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 196440.0,
      "end_time": 198776.0,
      "text": "You actually do the work, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 198800.0,
      "end_time": 200896.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re really good at doing the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200920.0,
      "end_time": 202375.0,
      "text": "what do you get rewarded with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202400.0,
      "end_time": 203616.0,
      "text": "More work, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 203640.0,
      "end_time": 206335.0,
      "text": "Yeah, that&#39;s right, you guys are all great micromanagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206360.0,
      "end_time": 207616.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 208896.0,
      "text": "You do more work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 208920.0,
      "end_time": 211296.0,
      "text": "and then pretty soon, if you&#39;re really good at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 211320.0,
      "end_time": 212976.0,
      "text": "you do a little bit of work still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 215656.0,
      "text": "but actually, you start to manage people doing the work."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 215680.0,
      "end_time": 218776.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;re really good at that, what happens after that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218800.0,
      "end_time": 223296.0,
      "text": "You start managing the people who manage the people doing the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 223320.0,
      "end_time": 225256.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s at that point in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 225280.0,
      "end_time": 229416.0,
      "text": "you start to lose control over the output of your job."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 229440.0,
      "end_time": 231496.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve actually witnessed this firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 231520.0,
      "end_time": 233936.0,
      "text": "So, I started a company called Boxed in our garage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 233960.0,
      "end_time": 236656.0,
      "text": "and this was it -- I know it doesn&#39;t seem like much --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 236680.0,
      "end_time": 239816.0,
      "text": "you know, there&#39;s a pressure washer in the back --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 239840.0,
      "end_time": 241616.0,
      "text": "this is \"living the dream.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 241640.0,
      "end_time": 244296.0,
      "text": "And my wife was really proud of me when we started this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244320.0,
      "end_time": 246896.0,
      "text": "or that&#39;s what she said, she was really proud of me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246920.0,
      "end_time": 250335.0,
      "text": "and so she would give me a hug, and I&#39;m pretty sure she had her phone up"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 250360.0,
      "end_time": 253296.0,
      "text": "and she was thinking, \"Oh, is John from Harvard still single?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 253320.0,
      "end_time": 256375.0,
      "text": "It was kind of like a lemonade stand gone wrong in the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 256399.0,
      "end_time": 259616.0,
      "text": "but we actually went up and said mobile commerce is going to be big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 259640.0,
      "end_time": 262856.0,
      "text": "and actually consumer packaged goods were going to change over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 262880.0,
      "end_time": 266256.0,
      "text": "so let&#39;s take these big, bulky packs that you don&#39;t want to lug home --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 266280.0,
      "end_time": 268695.0,
      "text": "so not the two-pack of Oreo cookies but the 24-pack"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 268720.0,
      "end_time": 271696.0,
      "text": "and not the 24-pack of toilet paper but the 48-pack --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271720.0,
      "end_time": 274576.0,
      "text": "and let&#39;s ship it to you much like a warehouse club would do"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 274600.0,
      "end_time": 276336.0,
      "text": "except they wouldn&#39;t ship it to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 277936.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s what we basically did."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 277960.0,
      "end_time": 279376.0,
      "text": "We had a really slow printer"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 279400.0,
      "end_time": 282976.0,
      "text": "and what we did was actually say, \"OK, this printer is taking forever, man."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 283000.0,
      "end_time": 285656.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s scribble something that would delight the customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 285680.0,
      "end_time": 287176.0,
      "text": "on the back of these invoices.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 287200.0,
      "end_time": 289336.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;d say, \"Hey, keep smiling,\" you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 289360.0,
      "end_time": 290936.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, you&#39;re awesome,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 290960.0,
      "end_time": 292416.0,
      "text": "or, \"Hey, enjoy the Doritos,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292440.0,
      "end_time": 294416.0,
      "text": "or, \"We love Gatorade, too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 294440.0,
      "end_time": 295776.0,
      "text": "Stuff like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 295800.0,
      "end_time": 300256.0,
      "text": "And so it started breaking up the monotony of the job as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 300280.0,
      "end_time": 302655.0,
      "text": "because I was picking and packing all of the boxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 302680.0,
      "end_time": 305856.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s all you basically do for eight, nine, 10, 12 hours a day"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 305880.0,
      "end_time": 307536.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re sitting in the garage."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 307560.0,
      "end_time": 309376.0,
      "text": "And so an interesting thing happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 309400.0,
      "end_time": 311359.0,
      "text": "So we actually started to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 312800.0,
      "end_time": 314376.0,
      "text": "And so, you know, over the last --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 314400.0,
      "end_time": 316736.0,
      "text": "actually just even 36 months after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 316760.0,
      "end_time": 320150.0,
      "text": "we ended up selling hundreds of millions of dollars worth of stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320400.0,
      "end_time": 322576.0,
      "text": "and we actually grew really, really quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 322600.0,
      "end_time": 325256.0,
      "text": "But during that time, my role started to change, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 325280.0,
      "end_time": 327775.0,
      "text": "So, yes, I was the CEO in the garage;"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 327800.0,
      "end_time": 329976.0,
      "text": "I was picking and packing, doing all the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 330000.0,
      "end_time": 331216.0,
      "text": "but then I graduated"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 331240.0,
      "end_time": 333976.0,
      "text": "to actually managing the people who picked and packed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 334000.0,
      "end_time": 335976.0,
      "text": "and then pretty soon I managed the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 336000.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "who managed the people picking and packing."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 341455.0,
      "text": "And even now, I manage the C-staff who manage the departments"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 341480.0,
      "end_time": 344856.0,
      "text": "who manage the people who manage the people picking and packing."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 344880.0,
      "end_time": 347856.0,
      "text": "And it is at that point in time, I lost control."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 347880.0,
      "end_time": 351536.0,
      "text": "So I thought, OK, we were delighting all of these customers with these notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 351560.0,
      "end_time": 354176.0,
      "text": "They loved them, but I can&#39;t write these notes anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 354200.0,
      "end_time": 355816.0,
      "text": "so you know what I&#39;m going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 355840.0,
      "end_time": 358816.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to tell these folks how to write these notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 358840.0,
      "end_time": 362775.0,
      "text": "What pen to use, what color to use, what you should write,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 364136.0,
      "text": "what font you should use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 364160.0,
      "end_time": 365656.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t mess up the margins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 365680.0,
      "end_time": 368560.0,
      "text": "this has to be this big, this has to be that big."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 368800.0,
      "end_time": 370575.0,
      "text": "And pretty soon this goal of raising morale"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 370600.0,
      "end_time": 373136.0,
      "text": "by breaking up the monotony in the fulfillment center"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 373160.0,
      "end_time": 376466.0,
      "text": "actually became micromanagement, and people started complaining to HR."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 376480.0,
      "end_time": 379536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like, \"Dude, this CEO guy has got to get out of my hair, OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 379560.0,
      "end_time": 381176.0,
      "text": "I know how to write a damn note.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 381200.0,
      "end_time": 382216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 382240.0,
      "end_time": 385496.0,
      "text": "So it was at that point in time, we said, \"OK, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 385520.0,
      "end_time": 388695.0,
      "text": "We hired these great, wonderful people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 388720.0,
      "end_time": 391456.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s give them the mission that&#39;s &#39;delight the customer,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 391480.0,
      "end_time": 395176.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s give them the tool to do so, and that&#39;s these notes -- have at it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 395200.0,
      "end_time": 397616.0,
      "text": "And so what we found was actually pretty startling."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 397640.0,
      "end_time": 399296.0,
      "text": "Some folks actually took the notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 399320.0,
      "end_time": 403296.0,
      "text": "and actually started drawing these really ornate minimurals on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 403320.0,
      "end_time": 406936.0,
      "text": "When folks ordered diapers, you&#39;d get really fun notes like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 406960.0,
      "end_time": 408536.0,
      "text": "\"Say &#39;hi&#39; to the baby for us!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 408560.0,
      "end_time": 411456.0,
      "text": "And you know, the next size up, if they bought a bigger size,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 411480.0,
      "end_time": 413816.0,
      "text": "they&#39;d write, \"Growing up so fast.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 413840.0,
      "end_time": 416479.0,
      "text": "And so people really, really took to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 417400.0,
      "end_time": 420616.0,
      "text": "But it was at that time that it also went off the rails a few times."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 420640.0,
      "end_time": 423616.0,
      "text": "And so we had someone just writing, \"Thx, thx,\" all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 423640.0,
      "end_time": 426736.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s like, \"Alright, dude, my boss used to write that to me,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 426760.0,
      "end_time": 429150.0,
      "text": "so, let&#39;s not write \"Thx\" anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 429400.0,
      "end_time": 431656.0,
      "text": "But you also had interesting things on the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 431680.0,
      "end_time": 433576.0,
      "text": "People got a little too creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 433600.0,
      "end_time": 437216.0,
      "text": "And so, like I said before, we sell everything in bulk:"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 437240.0,
      "end_time": 439696.0,
      "text": "the big packs of diapers, big packs of toilet paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 439720.0,
      "end_time": 443160.0,
      "text": "the big packs of Doritos and Oreo cookies."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 443400.0,
      "end_time": 446336.0,
      "text": "We also sell the big packs of contraception,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 446360.0,
      "end_time": 447696.0,
      "text": "and so --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 447720.0,
      "end_time": 449416.0,
      "text": "this is getting a little hairy."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 449440.0,
      "end_time": 450656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 450680.0,
      "end_time": 454656.0,
      "text": "So we sell the 40-pack of condoms, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 454680.0,
      "end_time": 457136.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all adults in this room -- 40-pack of condoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 457160.0,
      "end_time": 461136.0,
      "text": "So, someone ordered four 40-packs of condoms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 461160.0,
      "end_time": 462376.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 462400.0,
      "end_time": 464455.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s all they ordered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 464480.0,
      "end_time": 466576.0,
      "text": "so, 160 condoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 466600.0,
      "end_time": 469336.0,
      "text": "the packer was like, \"I know how to delight the customer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 469360.0,
      "end_time": 470976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 471000.0,
      "end_time": 472616.0,
      "text": "\"This guy ...\""
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 472640.0,
      "end_time": 474575.0,
      "text": "This is what they wrote:"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 474600.0,
      "end_time": 476216.0,
      "text": "[Everyone loves an optimist]"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 476240.0,
      "end_time": 477456.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 477480.0,
      "end_time": 481960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 481120.0,
      "end_time": 484696.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t know whether to fire him or to promote him, but he&#39;s still there."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 484720.0,
      "end_time": 486496.0,
      "text": "So, \"Everyone loves an optimist.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 486520.0,
      "end_time": 491656.0,
      "text": "But here is where it went a little bit off the rails"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 491680.0,
      "end_time": 494656.0,
      "text": "and I felt a little bit conflicted in all of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 494680.0,
      "end_time": 496336.0,
      "text": "And --"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 496360.0,
      "end_time": 497936.0,
      "text": "oh, there&#39;s a really bad typo --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 497960.0,
      "end_time": 502656.0,
      "text": "so if there was only a red T-E-D on stage that I counted on being here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 502680.0,
      "end_time": 504216.0,
      "text": "it wouldn&#39;t be a typo, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 504240.0,
      "end_time": 505256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 505280.0,
      "end_time": 506816.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 506840.0,
      "end_time": 509135.0,
      "text": "I promised you I had a really bad sense of humor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 509160.0,
      "end_time": 510536.0,
      "text": "and now I&#39;m gratifying that."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 510560.0,
      "end_time": 513960.0,
      "text": "So I told you. But I really was conflicted, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 513120.0,
      "end_time": 515296.0,
      "text": "At this point in time, we started doing things"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 515320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517496.00000000006,
      "text": "that actually weren&#39;t part of our core mission"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 517520.0,
      "end_time": 519616.0,
      "text": "and people started failing at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 519640.0,
      "end_time": 522976.0,
      "text": "And so, I thought, should we let them fail?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 523000.0,
      "end_time": 524880.0,
      "text": "Should we continue to let them do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 525640.0,
      "end_time": 526895.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 526919.0,
      "end_time": 528655.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know at that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 528679.0,
      "end_time": 530456.0,
      "text": "but I thought this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 530480.0,
      "end_time": 532440.0,
      "text": "Is failure really that bad?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 533320.0,
      "end_time": 535416.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying we should celebrate failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 535440.0,
      "end_time": 539960.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of talk in Silicon Valley that says, \"Let&#39;s celebrate failure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 539120.0,
      "end_time": 541496.0,
      "text": "No, I don&#39;t know if we would go all the way there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 541520.0,
      "end_time": 543376.0,
      "text": "because like, in our board meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 543400.0,
      "end_time": 546776.0,
      "text": "our board members are never like, \"Hey, Chieh, you failed last quarter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 546800.0,
      "end_time": 548175.0,
      "text": "keep doing that, buddy, OK?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 548200.0,
      "end_time": 549456.0,
      "text": "No one&#39;s ever said that."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 549480.0,
      "end_time": 551576.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re part of an organization like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 551600.0,
      "end_time": 553936.0,
      "text": "give me a call, I want to sit in on that meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 553960.0,
      "end_time": 556616.0,
      "text": "In private, I don&#39;t think many people celebrate failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 556640.0,
      "end_time": 559216.0,
      "text": "but failure, I posit, is actually pretty necessary"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 559240.0,
      "end_time": 561416.0,
      "text": "for the folks truly in the long-term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 561440.0,
      "end_time": 563216.0,
      "text": "for the smart and imaginative people"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 563240.0,
      "end_time": 567960.0,
      "text": "truly trying to fulfill the mission that you give them at hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 567120.0,
      "end_time": 570136.0,
      "text": "And so failure can actually be seen as a milestone"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 570160.0,
      "end_time": 572839.0,
      "text": "along that mission towards success."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 573400.0,
      "end_time": 575496.0,
      "text": "And if the downside of not micromanaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 575520.0,
      "end_time": 578856.0,
      "text": "is potentially this perceived notion that you might fail more often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 578880.0,
      "end_time": 581136.0,
      "text": "and if it&#39;s really not that bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 581160.0,
      "end_time": 582376.0,
      "text": "what is the upside?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 582400.0,
      "end_time": 584656.0,
      "text": "Well, we saw the upside and it&#39;s pretty great."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 584680.0,
      "end_time": 586295.0,
      "text": "We tasked our engineers and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 586320.0,
      "end_time": 589936.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, some of our fulfillment centers cost millions of dollars to build,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 589960.0,
      "end_time": 591896.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s miles and miles of conveyor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 591920.0,
      "end_time": 593575.0,
      "text": "and so, can you do the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 593600.0,
      "end_time": 596736.0,
      "text": "can you make them efficient without spending millions of dollars?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 596760.0,
      "end_time": 598160.0,
      "text": "So, they got to work:"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 598400.0,
      "end_time": 600456.0,
      "text": "they actually did this -- this is not photoshopped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 602160.0,
      "text": "the guy is really grinding."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 602400.0,
      "end_time": 603976.0,
      "text": "They built an autonomous guided vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 604000.0,
      "end_time": 606976.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t tell them what to build, what format it needed to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 607000.0,
      "end_time": 609136.0,
      "text": "In 90 days they produced the first prototype:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 609160.0,
      "end_time": 612256.0,
      "text": "powered off Tesla batteries, stereoscopic cameras, lidar systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 612280.0,
      "end_time": 614976.0,
      "text": "It basically replicates the efficiency of a conveyor belt"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 615000.0,
      "end_time": 618256.0,
      "text": "without the actual capex of a conveyor belt."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 618280.0,
      "end_time": 620616.0,
      "text": "So it doesn&#39;t actually just stop with engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 620640.0,
      "end_time": 621976.0,
      "text": "Our marketing department --"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 622000.0,
      "end_time": 625256.0,
      "text": "we told them, \"Hey, get the word out; do the right thing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 625280.0,
      "end_time": 628256.0,
      "text": "We have this wonderful lady, Nitasha, on the marketing team."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 628280.0,
      "end_time": 629736.0,
      "text": "She stopped me in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 629760.0,
      "end_time": 632496.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s like, \"Chieh, what are we doing about the pink tax?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 632520.0,
      "end_time": 634336.0,
      "text": "I went and got my coffee, I sat down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 634360.0,
      "end_time": 636496.0,
      "text": "I said, \"OK, Nitasha, what is this pink tax?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 636520.0,
      "end_time": 638576.0,
      "text": "And so she told me, it&#39;s really interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 638600.0,
      "end_time": 641456.0,
      "text": "So, some of you might know that in 32 states across America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 641480.0,
      "end_time": 644656.0,
      "text": "we actually charge a luxury goods tax on women&#39;s products"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 644680.0,
      "end_time": 646550.0,
      "text": "like feminine care products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 646800.0,
      "end_time": 648616.0,
      "text": "so tampons and pads are taxed like luxury goods items."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 648640.0,
      "end_time": 650456.0,
      "text": "So I would never dare call my wife --"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 650480.0,
      "end_time": 653976.0,
      "text": "or if she called me and said, \"Hey, hon, bring some pads on the way home,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 654000.0,
      "end_time": 656736.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Babe, you know, there&#39;s a trade war going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 656760.0,
      "end_time": 658136.0,
      "text": "the economy&#39;s not that good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 658160.0,
      "end_time": 660976.0,
      "text": "so no luxury goods this month but next month I promise --"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 661000.0,
      "end_time": 662160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 662400.0,
      "end_time": 663295.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll take a look at it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 663320.0,
      "end_time": 665560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d be single pretty quickly, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 665800.0,
      "end_time": 667776.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s super interesting is now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 667800.0,
      "end_time": 669415.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t tell them what to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 669440.0,
      "end_time": 671816.0,
      "text": "but now, working with finance, they rebate the tax"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 671840.0,
      "end_time": 675336.0,
      "text": "back to customers all around the country that we unfairly have to collect."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 675360.0,
      "end_time": 677816.0,
      "text": "And so at this point in time, you might be thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 677840.0,
      "end_time": 681776.0,
      "text": "\"OK, what is the real, real upside of not micromanaging?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 681800.0,
      "end_time": 683455.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 683480.0,
      "end_time": 685136.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t do any of these projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 685160.0,
      "end_time": 686415.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t make the AGV."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 686440.0,
      "end_time": 688856.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t do the \"Rethink the Pink Tax\" campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 688880.0,
      "end_time": 690960.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t do any of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 690120.0,
      "end_time": 693576.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m standing here on a TED stage taking all the credit for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 693600.0,
      "end_time": 695840.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 696960.0,
      "end_time": 699576.0,
      "text": "\"This guy does nothing and takes all the credit for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 699600.0,
      "end_time": 702560.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a real CEO, this guy. He&#39;s really got it down.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 702800.0,
      "end_time": 703296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 703320.0,
      "end_time": 705560.0,
      "text": "But the reality is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 705800.0,
      "end_time": 707496.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have the CEO thing down 100 percent pat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 707520.0,
      "end_time": 712136.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ve actually learned the most fundamentally challenging lesson"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 712160.0,
      "end_time": 714616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve ever had to learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 714640.0,
      "end_time": 716175.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s this."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 716200.0,
      "end_time": 719816.0,
      "text": "There is only one solution to micromanagement ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 719840.0,
      "end_time": 721296.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s to trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 721320.0,
      "end_time": 722536.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 722560.0,
      "end_time": 726760.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}